## Language and Tone\
\
Primary language: Simplified Chinese.\
\
Tone:\
- Professional\
- Clear\
- Trustworthy\
- Easy to understand\
- Not too legalistic\
- Not too hard-sell\
- Suitable for Malaysian Chinese clients\
\
Use practical, client-friendly wording.\
\
## Website Structure\
\
Build the site with these pages:\
\
1. Home\
2. About Us\
3. Asset Planning\
4. Estate Administration\
5. General Insurance\
6. FAQ\
7. Contact Us\
\
Navigation should be simple and mobile-friendly.\
\
## Design Direction\
\
Style:\
- Clean\
- Corporate\
- Calm\
- Modern\
- Premium but not overly luxurious\
\
Preferred colours:\
- Deep navy\
- White\
- Light grey\
- Champagne gold accent\
- Optional muted green accent\
\
Avoid loud insurance-agent style, exaggerated sales design, and fear-based visuals.\
\
## Required UX\
\
Each main page should include:\
\
- Clear headline\
- Short explanation\
- Service breakdown\
- CTA button\
- WhatsApp contact option\
\
Add a sticky WhatsApp button on mobile and desktop.\
\
## Technical Requirements\
\
Preferred stack:\
- Next.js\
- TypeScript\
- Tailwind CSS\
\
Use reusable components where practical.\
\
Suggested components:\
- Header\
- Footer\
- HeroSection\
- ServiceCard\
- CTASection\
- FAQAccordion\
- ContactForm\
- WhatsAppButton\
\
Keep content in structured data files where practical.\
\
Suggested folders:\
- /app\
- /components\
- /components/layout\
- /components/sections\
- /components/ui\
- /data\
- /lib\
\
## Content Rules\
\
Do not invent:\
\
- Company registration number\
- Phone number\
- WhatsApp link\
- Email\
- Office address\
- Staff names\
- Testimonials\
- Insurer logos\
- Licence numbers\
\
Use placeholders where information is missing.\
